reviewText: A gift for my mother, she loves watching these shows. She told me the quality is great and no issues with the subtitles being crappy.
Hello i love this tv series drama because Moon and Seo are in the show its very good and keeps you wanting to watch more great show must get for South Korean tv show fans.
I absolutely love this drama. The acting is perfect. First time I watched it I had to fight myself to stop watching and go to sleep.
